    <h2>Development Information</h2>
    <p>This website was written in Ruby, implementing the Rails framework. It utilizes Steam OpenID for functions such as the login page, and also utilizes the SteamAPI for features such as backpack viewing, etc. The forums are powered by an amazing engine for Rails called <a href="https://github.com/radar/forem">Forem.</a></p>
